### Secondary Sector

*Importance*: Income generated in the Secondary sector was 28.45 percent of GVA in the latest quarter. This can be compared with the Secondary sector's 28.35 percent share of GVA over the full data period.


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
![](index_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=672}
